{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"with-param","mdn_url":"/fr/docs/Web/XSLT/Element/with-param","locale":"fr","native":"Français","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">Référence XSLT/XPath</a></b> : <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">Éléments XSLT</a>, <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/EXSLT\">Fonctions EXSLT</a>, <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">Fonctions XPath</a>, <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">Axes XPath</a>\n</div>\n<p>L'élément <code>&lt;xsl:with-param&gt;</code> définit la valeur d'un paramètre à passer à un modèle.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntaxe","title":"Syntaxe","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">xsl:</span>with-param</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>NOM</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">select</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>EXPRESSION</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  MODÈLE\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token namespace\">xsl:</span>with-param</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribut_obligatoire","title":"Attribut obligatoire","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"name\"><code>name</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Définit un nom pour ce paramètre.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribut_optionnel","title":"Attribut optionnel","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"select\"><code>select</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Définit la valeur du paramètre à l'aide d'une expression XPath. Si l'élément contient un modèle, l'attribut est ignoré.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"type","title":"Type","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Sous-instruction, apparaît toujours dans un élément <code>&lt;xsl:apply-templates&gt;</code> ou un élément <code>&lt;xsl:call-template&gt;</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"définition","title":"Définition","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xslt#section-Passing-Parameters-to-Templates\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XSLT 1.0, section 11.6</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"support_gecko","title":"Support Gecko","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Supporté.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"L'élément <xsl:with-param> définit la valeur d'un paramètre à passer à un modèle.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<xsl:with-param>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"with-param","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<xsl:with-param>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"with-param","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"fr/web/xslt/element/with-param","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/fr/web/xslt/element/with-param/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web","title":"Technologies web pour développeurs"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/XSLT","title":"XSLT"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/XSLT/Element","title":"Éléments"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/XSLT/Element/with-param","title":"with-param"}],"pageTitle":"with-param - XSLT | MDN","noIndexing":false}}